Package: japanstat
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Easy Use of e-Stat API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Mizuki", "Uchida", email = "uchidamizuki@vivaldi.net", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for using the API of e-Stat, a portal site for Japanese government statistics.
